This is an awesome collaboration between me (Amuness Creeps) and daveyoufool.

No but seriously I hate my alarm clock.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Project Time:  15 days1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Image Credits:  All images belong to me
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Credit for Critique:  Doctor Cimmerian, Cyclopian, psul, deku_link, ahbonjour, and Fantem.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Post:  I hate my alarm clock. I hate it very much.  And this is the one way I could show my hatred for it. And we all know that feeling. It's early in the morning, you don't want to wake up because being in your subconscious is better than being in reality. But then the stupid little machinery that mankind has made awakes you. The alarm clock.

And what better way to tell that is from the crazy adventures in Site-48! Also, D-1169 is gonna die a lot. Why? As a gag I have planned for the future. Kinda like Kenny from South Park.

EDIT: OMG. I just woke up and a ton of people had upvoted and downvoted enough that they neutralized each others votes.funny how life works.

EDIT2: I think I got the tagging right. If not, then staff can clear it

